<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="scrapbook-gallery">
    <div class="polaroid p1">
      <div class="tape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/images/polaroid-1.avif" type="image/avif" />
        <img src="/images/polaroid-1.webp" alt="Specialty Coffee brewing" width="400" height="200" fetchpriority="high" />
      </picture>
      <div class="polaroid-text">The Perfect Brew</div>
    </div>
    <div class="polaroid p2">
      <div class="tape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/images/polaroid-2.avif" type="image/avif" />
        <img src="/images/polaroid-2.webp" alt="Delicious Chocolate Cake" width="400" height="200" fetchpriority="high" />
      </picture>
      <div class="polaroid-text">Baking Happiness</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text-block">
    <h2>The Story Behind<br /><span class="highlight">Our Flavors</span></h2>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>Coffee Cakes</strong>, nestled beautifully on the Thiruvananthapuram - Neyyar Dam Road, Kattakada. We are not just a cafe; we are a warm culinary experience.</p>
    <p>Our space is custom-designed to inspire rich conversations over every cup of specialty coffee. From our decadent chocolate cakes to our warm, flaky savory bites, everything is crafted locally with ultimate care and passion.</p>
    <p class="handwritten" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">&ldquo;Where rich specialty coffee meets sweet cravings and custom baking art.&rdquo;</p>
  </div>
</section>
